Mark Lowe, 32, from Skelmersdale, Lancashire, is serving a five-year sentence for beating and kicking his brother Wayne to death after he tried to stab him during a drink-fuelled day of fighting .
Mark then kicked Wayne, 33, to death and was charged with his murder .
His wife Sarah is now looking after three young children alone and said: 'Mark will regret what he did for the rest of his life, because he loved his brother'